## Earth System Model: IFS-FESOM2-SR

IFS-FESOM2-SR (2023): 
aerosol: none, prescribed MACv2-SP
atmos: IFS (IFS CY48R1, Tco1279, cubic octahedral reduced Gaussian grid; 137 levels)
atmosChem: none
land: none
landIce: none/prescribed
ocean: FESOM2 (FESOM; 5 km; 70 levels; top grid cell 0-10m)
ocnBgchem: none
seaIce: none

 ## Experiment: eerie-control-1950

coupled control with fixed 1950's forcing (HighResMIP equivalent of pre-industrial control)

[Imprint](https://www.dkrz.de/en/about-en/contact/impressum) and 
[Privacy Policy](https://www.dkrz.de/en/about-en/contact/en-datenschutzhinweise).
